{"type": "article", "id": 15173, "title": "可组装的儿童车", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-21T07:39:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000331FqpoKHzhTR7f9wUO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t荷兰设计师 Spencer Rotting和Sander Letema推出了一款可组装的儿童车“infento”，它包括各种细致的零件，可以根据需要组装成40种不同类型的小车或滑板。能够伴随儿童年龄的增长做出相应调整，成人也可以组成小型的交通工具。此外，所有的配件都采用无害的材料，以确保安全。<a href=\"http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/infento/infento-worlds-first-real-constructible-rides\" target=\"_blank\">这款车之前在众筹</a>，预计明年上市。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142441yDcGS7ohHgqaWwJP.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"355\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.43398533\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142442GpdeMfwTNWuoIJY4.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"345\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.42176039\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142442WYhsmbFBa8QOr6c1.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"642\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.78484108\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142443naAjCcHqmRus0Ndv.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142443E7SD9qvVG1RQkyZt.jpg\" width=\"680\" height=\"1007\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.48088235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}